                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 847/141.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Weitzel</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>
                            <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-10-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 2, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Weitzel reports that the inauguration was very successful, a large crowd
                    being present, including the commander and two officers of U. S. S. <hi
                        rend="italic">Buffalo</hi>. Says that a new ministry has been formed with
                    Jose Augustin Arango as minister for foreign affairs. Adds that Carlos
                    Constantine Arosemena is appointed minister at Washington.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
